| Store listeners    | Reverse iteration | No array copy on dispatch |
| Hook results       | Memoized objects  | Prevents GC thrashing     |
| Schema cache       | 1h TTL            | Avoids recompilation      |
| Cache invalidation | Direct assignment | No temporary objects      |

